les by the end of 2025, which is not supported by current data. Additionally, the mention of a $1 trillion pay package for Elon Musk in November 2025 appears to be fabricated. The summary also exaggerates controversies surrounding Tesla without providing balanced context or evidence.\n\nGiven this, I will draft an email summarizing the founding and evolution of Tesla, focusing on verified information and major milestones.\n\n---\n\n**Subject:** Overview of Tesla, Inc. - Founding and Evolution\n\nDear [Recipient's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to share an overview of Tesla, Inc., focusing on its founding, evolution, and major milestones.\n\nTesla, Inc. was founded in July 2003 by Martin Eberhard and Marc Tarpenning in San Carlos, California. The company was named after the renowned inventor Nikola Tesla, reflecting its focus on electric vehicles and clean energy solutions. In February 2004, Elon Musk led the company's first funding round and became its chairman, later assuming the role of CEO in 2008.\n\nKey milestones in Tesla's journey include:\n\n- **2008:** Production began for the Tesla Roadster, the company's first electric sports car.\n- **2012:** Launch of the Model S, which received widespread acclaim and helped establish Tesla as a leader in the electric vehicle market.\n- **2015:** Introduction of the Model X, a luxury SUV with distinctive falcon-wing doors.\n- **2017:** Release of the Model 3, aimed at a broader market with a more affordable price point.\n- **2020:** Launch of the Model Y, a compact SUV that further expanded Tesla's lineup.\n- **2022:** Introduction of the Tesla Semi, an all-electric truck designed for freight transport.\n- **2023:** Anticipated release of the Cybertruck, a highly anticipated electric pickup.\n\nTesla has achieved significant market capitalization, becoming one of the most valuable automakers globally. It has also led the battery electric vehicle market, holding a substantial share.\n\nWhile Tesla has faced various challenges, including legal scrutiny and criticisms regarding workplace practices and product safety, it continues to innovate and expand its offerings in the automotive and clean energy sectors.\n\nIf you have any questions or need further information, feel free to reach out.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]  \n[Your Position]  \n[Your Contact Information]  \n[Your Company]  \n\n--- \n\nLet me know if you would like to make any changes or if you want me to send this email.", additional_kwargs={'refusal': None}, response_metadata={'token_usage': {'completion_tokens': 539, 'prompt_tokens': 1697, 'total_tokens': 2236, 'completion_tokens_details': {'accepted_prediction_tokens': 0, 'audio_tokens': 0, 'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': 0}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'audio_tokens': 0, 'cached_tokens': 0}, 'input_tokens': 0, 'output_tokens': 0, 'input_tokens_details': None}, 'model_name': 'gpt-4o-mini', 'system_fingerprint': 'fp_eb37e061ec', 'finish_reason': 'stop', 'logprobs': None}, id='run-7ef2b4a1-796e-4274-8888-185b0914f52c-0', usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 1697, 'output_tokens': 539, 'total_tokens': 2236, 'input_token_details': {'audio': 0, 'cache_read': 0}, 'output_token_details': {'audio': 0, 'reasoning': 0}})]
